@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Content Moderation Policy";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h1 class="display-4"><i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i> Content Moderation Policy</h1>
        <p class="lead">Ensuring a Safe and Positive Community on ShareSmallBiz</p>
    </div>

    <section>
        <h2 class="h4"><i class="bi bi-info-circle"></i> Introduction</h2>
        <p>At <strong>ShareSmallBiz</strong>, we are committed to fostering a supportive and collaborative environment for small business owners. To maintain the integrity and safety of our community, we have established the following <strong>Content Moderation Policy</strong>. This policy outlines the guidelines for acceptable content and the procedures for moderation to ensure a positive experience for all members.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2 class="h4"><i class="bi bi-people"></i> 1. Acceptable Behavior</h2>
        <p>Members are expected to engage respectfully and professionally. The following behaviors are encouraged:</p>
        <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success"></i> <strong>Constructive Collaboration:</strong> Share insights, feedback, and resources that benefit the community.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success"></i> <strong>Respectful Communication:</strong> Interact with others courteously, valuing diverse perspectives.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success"></i> <strong>Authentic Content Sharing:</strong> Provide genuine and original content relevant to small business growth.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
        <h2 class="h4"><i class="bi bi-x-circle"></i> 2. Prohibited Content</h2>
        <p>To protect our community, the following content is strictly prohibited:</p>
        <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle text-danger"></i> <strong>Hate Speech and Discrimination:</strong> Any content promoting hatred, violence, or discrimination.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle text-danger"></i> <strong>Harassment and Bullying:</strong> Content that intimidates, threatens, or bullies members.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle text-danger"></i> <strong>Spam and Advertising:</strong> Unsolicited promotions or disruptive repetitive content.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle text-danger"></i> <strong>Illegal Activities:</strong> Encouraging or depicting illegal actions or prohibited goods/services.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle text-danger"></i> <strong>Misinformation:</strong> Sharing false or misleading information that could harm members.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
        <h2 class="h4"><i class="bi bi-shield-lock"></i> 3. Content Moderation Procedures</h2>
        <p>Our moderation team employs a combination of automated tools and human review to enforce these guidelines:</p>
        <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-robot text-primary"></i> <strong>Automated Monitoring:</strong> AI-driven tools detect and flag content violations.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-person-check text-primary"></i> <strong>Human Review:</strong> Moderators assess flagged content for guideline breaches.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-flag text-primary"></i> <strong>User Reporting:</strong> Members can report content for moderator evaluation.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
        <h2 class="h4"><i class="bi bi-gavel"></i> 4. Enforcement Actions</h2>
        <p>Violations may result in the following actions:</p>
        <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-trash text-danger"></i> <strong>Content Removal:</strong> Deleting violating content.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-person-dash text-warning"></i> <strong>Account Suspension:</strong> Temporarily restricting access for severe or repeated violations.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-person-x text-danger"></i> <strong>Account Termination:</strong> Permanent bans for egregious misconduct.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
        <h2 class="h4"><i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat"></i> 5. Appeals Process</h2>
        <p>Members can appeal moderation decisions by contacting our support team. Appeals will be reviewed, and decisions communicated promptly.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
        <h2 class="h4"><i class="bi bi-chat-dots"></i> 6. Community Etiquette</h2>
        <p>To maintain a positive environment, members should:</p>
        <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-emoji-smile text-success"></i> <strong>Be Respectful:</strong> Honor differing opinions and engage in civil discourse.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-chat-text text-success"></i> <strong>Stay On-Topic:</strong> Ensure contributions are relevant to small business topics.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><i class="bi bi-shield-slash text-success"></i> <strong>Protect Privacy:</strong> Avoid sharing personal or sensitive information without consent.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
        <h2 class="h4"><i class="bi bi-journal-code"></i> 7. Policy Updates</h2>
        <p>ShareSmallBiz reserves the right to modify this Content Moderation Policy as needed. Members will be notified of significant changes, and continued participation constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="alert alert-primary text-center mt-5" role="alert">
        <i class="bi bi-heart-fill"></i> Thank you for contributing to the positive atmosphere at <strong>ShareSmallBiz</strong>!
    </div>
</div>
